name: Individual Bars 03
description:
Individual Bars 03 with a seed based on the owners tezos-addresses, renders differently for every owner/viewer.
First rendering is always based on the viewer-wallet-address.

Click/Tap to cycle through the different versions of the different owners.

Uses the hicdex API and therefore depends on it. This is all experimental and might break in the future. OBJKT uses p5js with p5.createloop and post5.
- @TeNinEightNFTs
